Package: yachtvaa
Title: Paddler Performance Analysis with Environmental Conditions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Eduardo", "Leoni",
           email = "e.leoni@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0955-5232"))
Description: Integrates paddler GPS data from Treinus with SIMCOSTA buoy
    environmental measurements to analyze performance relative to wind and
    current conditions near Yacht Club da Bahia, Salvador, Brazil. Computes
    fastest straight-line distances, matches segments to interpolated buoy
    data, and builds league tables ranking athletes under varying conditions.
